-------------------------------------------
If you are unfamiliar using NANO, please
read the following guide carefully.

* To add or edit text, just type as normal
* Press Ctrl+O to save your work
* Press Ctrl+X to exit this session
* Press Alt+U to undo

After exiting the session you, and anyone
else for that matter, will NOT be able to
read, edit or remove your remark. Saving
using Ctrl+O is however unaffected.

Please comment below this line. When you
wish to submit your comment, simply save
and exit the current session.
-------------------------------------------
